.DS_Store

# Green Button exports and bills carry name, address, account and meter numbers.
# Never commit them; verify.mjs and the bill importer take a path as an argument.
# Bill filenames vary ("chris-Feb 2026.pdf", "SDGE_...bill.pdf"), so ignore every
# PDF rather than a "bill" pattern that misses most of them. The repo commits no
# PDFs; the vendored pdf.js library is .mjs, not .pdf.
*Electric_*.csv
*Electric_*.xml
*.pdf

# Written by the Pages workflow at deploy time, so the footer can name the
# commit it was built from. Committing it would guarantee it is stale.
build-info.json
